summary: An ordinance authorizing the dismissal of a suit to condemn private property for the laying off, extending, widening, altering, and establishing of a public street and highway from Arizona Avenue to West Spokane Street to 37th Avenue Southwest and West Wait Street; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues, under Ordinance No. 29062, Cause No. 91104; insofar as the same affects certain property in block 437, Seattle Tide Lands and in blocks 1, 2, and 3, Seaboard Addition to the City of Seattle.
